gw.plugin.billing

Class BillingTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.plugin.billing.BillingTransaction

  • public class BillingTransaction
extends java.lang.Object
    The BillingTransaction class provides:
    • The DateRecorded as a Date
    • The EffectiveDate as a Date
    • The TransactionType as a BillingTransactionType
    • The DebitAmount as a BigDecimal
    • The CreditAmount as a BigDecimal
    • The BillDocId as a String
